image.altText: Mesepa Salesa leaves court with Josh Papalii

props.synopsis: The wife of Canberra Raiders star Josh Papalii, Mesepa Salesa, is convicted of assault and handed a good behaviour order in the ACT Magistrates Court.

title.children: Mesepa Salesa, wife of Raiders star Josh Papalii, convicted of assault

image.altText: ACT Chief Police Officer Scott Lee in the Belconnen Police Station

props.synopsis: The ACT Chief Police Officer says the raising of the age of criminality in the territory from 12 to 14, due to take effect in July, will put pressure on police. He says services will need to be increased to relieve pressure.

title.children: Top cop says raised age of criminality in ACT will put pressure on police

image.altText: Ben Roberts-Smith wearing a blue shirt and white shirt with a tie

props.synopsis: Veteran Ben Roberts-Smith takes his legal battle with Nine Newspapers to the High Court.

title.children: 'A condemnation of the most ruinous kind': Ben Roberts-Smith appeals to High Court

image.altText: A worker wearing a hard hat with the CFMEU logo emblazoned across it.

props.synopsis: Former CFMEU officials lose a High Court challenge to changes to the Fair Work Act which forced the construction arm of the union into administration.

title.children: Former CFMEU officials fail to overturn federal government's takeover bid

image.altText: An indoor wall with lettering on it that reads "ACT Integrity Commission".

image.altText: An adult and a child walking across a pedestrian crossing in a school zone, with the bonnet of a car in the left foreground.

title.children: Would you accept a 30kph school zone speed limit?

image.altText: A man with short dark hair in a navy suit and tie looks down at a smartphone as he walks out of a courthouse.

title.children: 'Tell no-one': Man met 11yo alleged victim on dating app, court hears

image.altText: Ayatollah Ali Khamenei waves against a blue curtained background

title.children: Khamenei warns Trump Iran will 'not surrender' as Israel launches fresh strikes on Tehran

image.altText: optus 'yes' sign on glass fronted office block

image.altText: An image of Erin Patterson.

image.altText: Trump salutes while wearing red MAGA hat

image.altText: A man's forearm focused at the interior of the elbow with a needle injected withdrawing blood.
